Although using JSON for the request isn't configurable in flask-oauthlib you can work around it with: 

```
def json_to_form(f):
    @wraps(f)
    def _wrapper(*args, **kwargs):
        request.form = ImmutableMultiDict(request.json)
        return f(*args, **kwargs)
    return _wrapper


@blueprint.route('/oauth/token', methods=['POST'])
@json_to_form
@oauth2.token_handler
def access_token():
    return None
```

